GET info about SpaceX rockets

GET info about SpaceX rockets

get_SpaceX_rockets(name = NULL)

Arguments

name

character: Name of the rocket. Choose between "falcon1", "falcon9" or "falconheavy". By default all three rocket data are returned.

Value

data.frame with parsed data from SpaceX API.

Examples


## get details about all rockets
get_SpaceX_rockets()
